                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14490237" author="petersla" created="Fri, 10 Apr 2015 19:44:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached patch which fixes this issue by having CBZip2InputStream close the inner stream upon its close.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14527638" author="jeremykarn" created="Tue, 5 May 2015 00:33:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I just came across this bug and this patch seems to fix it for me.  Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14527691" author="petersla" created="Tue, 5 May 2015 00:58:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Glad to hear this patch helps! &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=olgan&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;olgan&quot;&gt;olgan&lt;/a&gt;, is there anyone that could take a look at this? Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14531370" author="daijy" created="Wed, 6 May 2015 20:44:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I will take a look.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14535133" author="petersla" created="Fri, 8 May 2015 18:08:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=daijy&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;daijy&quot;&gt;daijy&lt;/a&gt;, Thanks for taking a look!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14539397" author="daijy" created="Tue, 12 May 2015 06:58:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I cannot figure out why we set innerBsStream to null before, checking the use cases of CBZip2InputStream, apparently we shall close it instead of setting it to null. +1 for the patch, the only thing is missing Apache license header in the new file, I added it in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4496&quot; title=&quot;Fix CBZip2InputStream to close underlying stream&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-4496&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-4496&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;-2.patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14539402" author="daijy" created="Tue, 12 May 2015 07:01:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch committed to both 0.15 branch and trunk. Thanks Peter!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
